<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Zum tuah, zummi hna zum tuah, Dohnak saupi hmanhseh, Nannih nan luat
 kho te lai, Pathian bawmhnak thawngin. CHO: Zum tuah, zum tuah, Ningti
 khuamui hmanh seh, Zum tuah, zum tuah, Deirel a chuak deng cang.

[V2]
 Zum tuah, ral an kan dum ko, Tukforhnak a tamko; Pathian nih a kan
 bawmh lai, Lam kan palhnak hnga lo.

[V3]
 Bawipa nih a kan khamh khawh, Kan hawitha kha a si; Zum tuah, zummi
 hna zum tuah, A dongh tiang in zum tuah.</lyrics>
<key>F</key>
<title>ZUM TUAH CH324</title>
<hymn_number>324</hymn_number>
</song>